         <abstract>
            <p>Ortiz' step-by-step recursive formulation of the Lanczos tau method is extended to the numerical solution of linear systems of differential equations with polynomial coefficients. Numerical comparisons are made with Gear's and Enright's methods.</p>
          </abstract>
